罩俾啲醫護仲好啦"},{"pid":"2b95e29225b714e75d1a3ee386bf84f1158be2d2","tid":2008270,"uid":44224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ad17a0fdbd44d752f120c1eca76577993e6e125","tid":2008270,"uid":308262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"醫護唔用得csi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n規格唔夠高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"咁同市民交換得唔得<br />\n我要csi<br />\n唔要底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e28b38b64ff2728a3116b6c274ce9c2c87d53d","tid":2008270,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:35:41.000Z","msg":"【高手過招】政治專家教你打贏輿論戰 同藍絲鬧交成日鬧輸嘅你一定要睇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2005539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2005539</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n「如果美國要求中國就中共病毒賠償，中國一定會攞各位香港人血汗錢嚟找數」</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「如果啲一帶一路投資失敗啲非洲國家要賠償，中國一定都會攞各位香港人血汗錢嚟找數」<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">GET MY MONEY BACK<br />\n我要攞返我啲錢<br />\n香港人啲錢唔係比港共亂咁洗</span></span><br />\n香港納稅人財政儲備 不是中共提款機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要攞返我啲錢</span></strong></span>」就係我哋對攬炒嘅論述<br />\n「<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>如果這是攬炒，我們不怕承認</strong></span></span>」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港財政儲備絕對唔可以比中共當係提款機嚟用<br />\n唔可以攞嚟起啲濕鳩明日大嶼<br />\n唔可以攞嚟找一帶一路啲數 債務<br />\n更加唔可以攞香港啲錢嚟賠償中共病毒索償費用</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n高鐵已經有版我哋睇<br />\n高鐵造價853億沒有帶來經濟效益 卻只有贈送中共病毒（武漢肺炎）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-10_NQdC3_1200x0.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n攬抄 就是從港共手中搶返屬於我哋嘅血汗錢<br />\n<br />\n立法會35+之後就係要否決預算案<br />\n推冧港共之後再建立一個<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>民主主權國家<br />\n35+就是「罷免港共行動」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n中國係中共病毒疫情之後將會比全球杯葛<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聰明嘅香港人要及時止蝕同中國割席<br />\n因為一個獨立主權國家<br />\n係國際舞台先會有競爭力<br />\n先至可以同鄰近嘅星加坡，台灣一較高下</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港只要唔係獨立主權國家，人哋係唔撚會show你，亦都唔會有信心返嚟香港投資</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n攬炒就是<br />\n「從港共手中搶回屬於香港人金庫」<br />\n「建立獨立主權國家 民主政體 才是爭取國際競爭力的致勝之道」"},{"pid":"93657e7199349cc502f2676d28ea15dcc8b3e704","tid":2008270,"uid":44224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:01:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f878ee4b3d6bf2d7c91205500c469430aba9183c","tid":2008270,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6fcecbe38da15cbd5c86b698383aeede63efb14","tid":2008270,"uid":220431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:31:08.000Z","msg":"儲埋之後捐返比警狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"打完飛機射啲精落去先捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587def939002885d60692548bc254016bc0e5106","tid":2008270,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:03:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e13bebf892210986af77505957989bffcfac0a4e","tid":2008270,"uid":103719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:07:17.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"889f03b86a9d61ec3975d1c9440d538ad521037a","tid":2008270,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"老實講，唔好講話差佬，政府d人自己都唔帶返真係好難説服市民帶㗎播，一日未搞清楚會唔會銅入肺，我郵局都唔會去拎口罩囉"},{"pid":"e25cb454e79be20ce1ead3ab5dde9a3fab0c96f9","tid":2008270,"uid":342828,"l